title: Brett Stegmaier takes 1-shot lead in Las Vegas
text:
> Florida Brett Stegmaier takes 1-shot lead in Las Vegas Jason Bohn watches his tee shot on the first hole during the third round of the Shriners Hospitals for Children Open golf tournament Saturday, Oct. 24, 2015, in Las Vegas. (AP Photo/Isaac Brekken)
